Test Case 1 — Basic Example
Input
A = "abcdef"
B = "ghijklmnopqrst"
Output
agbhcjdlenfpqrst
________________________________________
Test Case 2 — Small Strings
Input
A = "ab"
B = "wxyz"
Process
•	A[0] → a
•	B[0] → w
•	A[1] → b
•	B[1] → x
Remaining B → yz
Output
awbxyz
________________________________________
Test Case 3 — Minimum Size A
Input
A = "a"
B = "bcdef"
Output
abcdef
________________________________________
Test Case 4 — B Index Skips Fast
Input
A = "abcd"
B = "mnopqrstuv"
B Indices Pattern
•	0
•	1
•	3
•	5
Output
ambncpdfrstuv
________________________________________
Test Case 5 — A Almost Reaches Limit
Input
A = "xyz"
B = "abcdefghijkl"
Output
xaybzdcfghijkl
________________________________________
Test Case 6 — Repeated Characters
Input
A = "aaa"
B = "bbbbbbbb"
Output
abababbbbb
________________________________________
⭐ Optional Hidden Edge Test (For Platforms)
Input
A = "mnopq"
B = "abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz"
Checks:
•	Correct B index calculation
•	Proper leftover B append
